{"id": 1246, "genre": 1001, "title": "你在洗澡的时候会有哪些特别的习惯？", "description": "一直拖延不去洗澡也是一种习惯，嗯。（题图来自：Carlos Arrojo）", "record_count": 5234, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160927151420f9GlZ2cIeuiVhWTE.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-09-29T03:00:53Z", "options": [{"id": 120576, "content": "放歌", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 686426}, {"id": 120577, "content": "一定要放点什么听 听歌啊 脱口秀啊 或者相声［相声发烧友的］", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 763947}, {"id": 121601, "content": "唱Leslie的歌", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 783024}, {"id": 120578, "content": "拖到最后一秒钟", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 776600}, {"id": 120579, "content": "当然是尿尿啊……", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 777494}, {"id": 120580, "content": "扯下蛋……", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 604282}, {"id": 121604, "content": "一沾水就要尿", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 782380}, {"id": 120581, "content": "我想要辞职", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 777498}, {"id": 120582, "content": "我去", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 777498}, {"id": 121350, "content": "没什么特别的习惯！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 780419}, {"id": 121606, "content": "冥想", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 783073}, {"id": 120583, "content": "high歌一曲。不会唱就哼", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 739476}, {"id": 321543, "content": "洗腿的时候把腿翘在墙上擦，省的弯腰", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1494436}, {"id": 120585, "content": "洗头\n香烟洗\n沐浴露洗\n^_^", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 737173}, {"id": 120586, "content": "刷牙", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 736046}, {"id": 121098, "content": "洗澡中90%时间考虑要不要赏赐自己洗个脸。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 778065}, {"id": 121610, "content": "先把全身打湿，在洗头。。。。通常头洗完的时候，水已经不够了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 767527}, {"id": 121866, "content": "一直不洗，不想洗", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 786638}, {"id": 120587, "content": "最后一步一定是站着洗脚！死劲搓......", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 777530}, {"id": 120588, "content": "只有一款沐浴液洗发露护发素不能忍，必须有几瓶，轮着来，同理牙膏和洗面奶。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 763962}, {"id": 121613, "content": "放音乐 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 783228}, {"id": 120590, "content": "撸管", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 774701}, {"id": 120591, "content": "不喜欢关门?算吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 777560}, {"id": 120592, "content": "抠", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 777568}, {"id": 120593, "content": "听个东西，相声，音乐，逻辑思维都可以、只要让我不会专注于洗澡这件事的就好…", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1226639}, {"id": 121361, "content": "唱歌", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 304274}, {"id": 125201, "content": "站着尿，跳热舞，唱歌", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 798604}, {"id": 134930, "content": "边洗澡边思考", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 833391}, {"id": 120594, "content": "开启无限自恋模式", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 777571}, {"id": 121362, "content": "洗脸，洗头，洗身体，不能乱，最后毛巾一定要热水先搓一下", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 780556}, {"id": 120595, "content": "有顺序：头，脸", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 740053}, {"id": 121107, "content": "一定要蜷缩身体", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 623377}, {"id": 125459, "content": "想蹲会儿马桶", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 796995}, {"id": 120596, "content": "思考人生", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 509422}, {"id": 120597, "content": "泡脚", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 53712}, {"id": 124437, "content": "会坐一下", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 796278}, {"id": 120598, "content": "用私处当泡沫球用\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 36, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 707291}, {"id": 121366, "content": "相比沐浴露更喜欢用香皂?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 780619}, {"id": 120343, "content": "冲背的时候习惯性思考人生", "image": null, "praise_count": 378, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 423413}, {"id": 120599, "content": "先上个便便", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 390149}, {"id": 121111, "content": "先洗脸，然后洗身，然後再洗头，这个顺序改不了?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 777312}, {"id": 121623, "content": "洗头时开着水龙头", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 783265}, {"id": 124439, "content": "会用花洒洗个脸", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 796278}, {"id": 120344, "content": "摸肚皮 如果吃得太撑会有负罪感", "image": null, "praise_count": 216, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 759982}, {"id": 121368, "content": "听音乐。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 780641}, {"id": 128792, "content": "靠着洗澡来解压，思考人生", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 815318}, {"id": 120345, "content": "先洗头，就酱", "image": null, "praise_count": 520, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 766939}, {"id": 120601, "content": "计划八点洗澡 结果十八点去洗澡", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 439933}, {"id": 121369, "content": "得尿尿，不然觉得缺点啥", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 780670}, {"id": 124185, "content": "喜欢蹲着或者坐在在地上淋", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 787439}]}